\sum_{k=1}^{\infty}a_{k}
\sum_{k=j}^{\infty}a_{k}
j>1
 \sum_{k=j}^\infty a_k = \sum_{k=1}^\infty a_k - \sum_{k=1}^{j-1}a_k. 
(a)
\sum_{k=j}^\infty a_k \quad=\quad \sum_{k=1}^\infty a_k \;\;- \;\;\sum_{k=1}^{j-1}a_k.\tag{1}
(1)
(1)
\;\displaystyle \sum_{k=j}^\infty a_k\;
\sum_{k=j}^{\infty}a_k=\sum_{k=1}^{\infty}a_k-(a_1+a_2+...+a_{j-1})
